{"ID":270310, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"310\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs309.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs311.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 310<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Baptism for the Dead Taught in New Testament<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The doctrine of baptism for the dead is clearly shown in the New Testament;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> and if the doctrine\n  is not good, then throw the New Testament away; but if it is the word of God, then let the doctrine\n  be acknowledged; and it was the reason why Jesus said unto the Jews, &ldquo;How oft would I have\n  gathered thy children together, even as a hen gathereth her chickens under her wings, and ye would\n  not!&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span>&mdash;that they might attend to the ordinances of baptism for the dead as well as other ordinances\n  of the priesthood, and receive revelations from heaven, and be perfected in the things of the kingdom\n  of God<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span>&mdash;but they would not.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> This was the case on the day of Pentecost:<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> those blessings were\n  poured out on the disciples on that occasion. God ordained that He would save the dead, and would\n  do it by gathering His people together.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The World of Spirits<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">It always has been when a man was sent of God with the priesthood and he began to preach the\n  fullness of the gospel,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> that he was thrust out by his friends,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> who are already to butcher him if he\n  teach things which they imagine to be wrong; and Jesus was crucified upon this principle.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I will now turn linguist. There are many things in the Bible which do not, as they now stand,\n  accord with the revelations of the Holy Ghost to me.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I will criticise a little further. There has been much said about the word hell, and the sectarian\n  world have preached much about it, describing it to be a burning lake of fire and brimstone.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> But\n  what is hell? It is another modern term, and is taken from hades. I&rsquo;ll hunt after hades as Pat did for\n  the woodchuck.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Hades, the Greek, or Sheol, the Hebrew, these two significations mean a world of spirits.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span>\n  Hades, Sheol, paradise,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> spirits in prison, are all one: it is a world of spirits.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The righteous and the wicked all go to the same world of spirits<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> until the resurrection. &ldquo;I do\n  not think so,&rdquo; says one. If you will go to my house any time, I will take my lexicon and prove it to\n  you.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The great misery of departed spirits in the world of spirits, where they go after death, is to know\n  that they come short<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> of the glory<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> that others enjoy and that they might have enjoyed<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109598\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109598)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109598)\">1 Cor. 15:29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108192\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108192)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108192)\">Matt. 23:37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114285\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114285)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114285)\">D&amp;C 67:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106483\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106483)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106483)\">2 Kgs. 17:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106537\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106537)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106537)\">2 Chr. 24:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107104\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107104)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107104)\">Isa. 28:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107338\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107338)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107338)\">Jer. 13:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107700\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107700)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107700)\">Zech. 7:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108152\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108152)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108152)\">Matt. 22:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108479\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108479)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108479)\">Luke 7:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110945\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110945)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110945)\">1 Ne. 8:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111638\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111638)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111638)\">Mosiah 16:2,12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111711\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111711)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111711)\">Mosiah 26:4,26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113298\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113298)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113298)\">D&amp;C 19:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114662\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114662)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114662)\">D&amp;C 84:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116796\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116796)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116796)\">Moses 5:57<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108916\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108916)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108916)\">Acts 2:1-4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113617\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113617)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113617)\">D&amp;C 35:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110902\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110902)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110902)\">1 Ne. 1:18-20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111215\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111215)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111215)\">2 Ne. 10:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108436\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108436)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108436)\">Luke 2:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113362\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113362)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113362)\">D&amp;C 20:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115764\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115764)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115764)\">D&amp;C 121:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110858\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110858)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110858)\">Rev. 20:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110875\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110875)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110875)\">Rev. 21:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111181\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111181)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111181)\">2 Ne. 9:16,19,26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114166\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114166)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114166)\">D&amp;C 63:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114425\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114425)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114425)\">D&amp;C 76:36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116675\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116675)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116675)\">D&amp;C 138:36,56-57<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112267\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112267)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112267)\">Alma 40:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112266\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112266)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112266)\">Alma 40:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116661\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116661)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116661)\">D&amp;C 138:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108542\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108542)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108542)\">Luke 16:19-31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110247\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110247)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110247)\">Heb. 10:26-27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111422\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111422)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111422)\">Jacob 6:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112277\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112277)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112277)\">Alma 40:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115315\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115315)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115315)\">D&amp;C 104:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109261\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109261)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109261)\">Rom. 3:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}